org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.meta

Class LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfgDefn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.opendj.config.AbstractManagedObjectDefinition<C,S>
      • org.forgerock.opendj.config.ManagedObjectDefinition<LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfgClient,LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfg>
        • org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.meta.LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfgDefn

  • public final class LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfgDefn
extends ManagedObjectDefinition<LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfgClient,LDAPKeyManagerProviderCfg>
    An interface for querying the LDAP Key Manager Provider managed object definition meta information.

    The LDAP key manager provider uses an LDAP key store managed by the server to obtain server certificates.
